<bibRefCitation author="Baselga, A. &amp; Recuero, G." box="[748,941,1336,1358]" pageId="4" pageNumber="690" pagination="5060 - 5073" refId="ref3648" refString="Baselga, A., E. Recuero, G. Parra-Olea, and M. Garc'ia Par'is. 2011. Phylogenetic patterns in zopherine beetles are related to ecological niche width and dispersal limitation. Molecular Ecology 20: 5060 - 5073." type="journal article" year="2011">
Baselga 
<emphasis box="[832,882,1336,1358]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="690">et al.</emphasis>
2011
</bibRefCitation>
). We add the following distributional data: “ 
<collectingCountry box="[888,985,1364,1385]" name="Mexico" pageId="4" pageNumber="690">MEXICO</collectingCountry>
: 
